title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 17 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 17 2021
description:
Fox's Brian Kilmeade on covid insanity, texting with Trump and others on Jan. 6th, and his new history book. Team EIB (and Texas Congressman Louie Gohmert) surprise Buck with an early birthday cake -- and CNN doesn't understand gas prices. Karol Markowicz, New York Post columnist, on why she left New York for Florida. The Hindenburg of vaccines and Build Back Bust.
